      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah. exactly. mcm exactly. it’s just... what is the point of carrying this around? it feels so hollow. like i'm just taking up space in a world that moved on from me years ago. i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. it's just this endless, empty loop.",
