      "content": "it's not even about \"change\" though. i don't think there's anything left to change. when you're just a ghost, how do you even interact with the real world anymore? it feels like i'm just lingering, being a nuisance to everyone around me by just existing. like, if the real me is gone, what's the purpose of keeping this shell around?",
